code: public boolean process(final Exchange exchange, final AsyncCallback callback) {     AsyncProcessor[] list = doGetProcessors().     if (list.length > 0) {         AsyncProcessor processor = chooseProcessor(list, exchange).         if (processor == null) {             Exception e = new IllegalStateException("No processors could be chosen to process " + exchange).             exchange.setException(e).         } else {             processor.process(exchange, callback).             return false.         }     }     // no processors but indicate we are done     callback.done(false).     return false. }
protected abstract AsyncProcessor chooseProcessor(AsyncProcessor[] processors, Exchange exchange).
